snippet.title: 666 Second Rule [ RELEASE TRAiLER ]
snippet.description:
🎮 Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2540110/666_Second_Rule/

666 Second Rule is a short action game where you take the role of a tormented parent battling relentless insects. Utilize dark powers to fend off their disturbing attempts to crawl into the baby's head.

❤️ Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/strayfeet
